## 1. Project Overview

| Field | Value |
|-------|-------|
| **Product Name** | DigiWash |
| **Tagline** | Smart Laundry-as-a-Service Platform for Market Merchants |
| **Product Type** | B2B SaaS — Vertical-integrated laundry + commerce platform |
| **Current Stack** | PHP 8 · MySQL · Vanilla JS · Razorpay · Firebase FCM · XAMPP |
| **Target Scale** | 50–500 merchants per market zone |
| **Deployment** | Self-hosted (XAMPP) → Cloud-ready (VPS/cPanel) |
| **Version** | 1.0 Production Candidate → v2.0 Enhanced Target |

### What DigiWash Does

DigiWash is a **B2B SaaS platform** for market merchants (shop owners) who need regular laundry services for their business linens — tablecloths, uniforms, curtains, bedsheets, etc. It digitizes the **entire laundry lifecycle**: scheduling pickups, tracking wash status, managing payments on credit, and delivering back cleaned items — all verifiable with PIN/QR proof-of-delivery.

DigiWash also bundles a **marketplace (DigiMarket)** for merchants to purchase laundry supplies (detergents, bedsheets, cleaning materials) directly through the platform, creating a full-stack commerce + service ecosystem.

---

## 2. Problem Statement

### Current Reality (Pain Points)

| # | Pain Point | Impact |
|---|-----------|--------|
| 1 | Laundry services for merchants are fully manual — phone calls, paper registers, no tracking | High disputes, lost items |
| 2 | Delivery partners have no visibility into routes, customer contacts, or order priority | Inefficient operations |
| 3 | No digital payment trail for laundry services — COD dominant, frequent credit disputes | Revenue leakage |
| 4 | Merchants buying laundry supplies go to separate stores — friction, no credit terms | Lost upsell revenue |
| 5 | Admins manage multiple drivers, zones, and orders manually via WhatsApp/phone | Operational chaos at scale |

### DigiWash Solution

- **Single platform** for end-to-end laundry order management with real-time GPS-linked delivery
- **Credit/Pay Later system** for trusted merchants — pay after 4/8/12 orders
- **Embedded marketplace** for laundry supply procurement with same delivery fleet
- **Proof-of-delivery** via PIN, QR, or photo bypass — eliminates disputes
- **Admin analytics dashboard** for revenue, delivery performance, and user trust scoring

