## 5. User Flow — End-to-End Journeys

### 5.1 New Customer Onboarding Flow

```
Visit landing page
    → Click "Login"
    → Enter phone number
    → [Rate limit check: max 5 OTP/10 min] ← NEEDS FIX
    → Receive OTP → Enter OTP → Verify
    → [Check is_blocked] ← NEEDS FIX
    → [First login?] → Setup Profile
        → Enter name, shop address
        → GPS detect location (lat/lng auto-fill)
        → Select market zone
        → Save → Redirect to Dashboard
    → [Returning user] → Dashboard (home section)
```

### 5.2 Laundry Order Flow (COD)

```
Dashboard → "New Order" tab
    → Browse product catalog (filterable)
    → Select items + quantities + sizes
    → Apply coupon (optional)
    → Select COD payment
    → [Server: check COD limit < 4 unpaid]
    → Submit → Order created (status: pending)
    → [Auto-assign: best online delivery partner in zone]
    → Customer toast: "Order placed! Driver assigned."
    → FCM push: "Order confirmed"
        Delivery partner notified
```

### 5.3 Marketplace Order Flow (Pay Later + PIN Delivery)

```
Marketplace tab → Browse products
    → Add to cart (simple products or per-meter bedsheets)
    → Cart review → Select "Pay Later (Credit)"
    → [Server: check credit eligibility + available slots]
    → Place order → marketplace_order created
    → Admin auto-assigns delivery partner
    → Delivery partner: "DigiMarket" tab in delivery dashboard
        → Mark Picked Up → Mark Out for Delivery
        → "Verify PIN to Deliver" button appears
        → Enter 6-digit PIN from customer dashboard
        → [Server: validate PIN against user_id + 30-min window]
        → Order marked "delivered", payment_status unchanged (paid later)
    → Customer sees delivery notification
    → Dashboard → Payments → Combined Credit Due shows marketplace amount
    → "Pay All Now" → Razorpay bulk checkout → all dues cleared
```

### 5.4 Combined Payment Flow

```
Dashboard → Payments tab
    → [Fetch laundry pending dues] + [Fetch marketplace pending dues] (parallel)
    → Show "DigiMarket — Pay Later Dues" banner (if any marketplace dues)
    → Show individual order cards (laundry + marketplace, excluding cancelled)
    → Show "Combined Credit Due" card with total
    → [Lock check: any order still in transit?]
        → Yes: "Pay All Now" disabled with "Waiting for Delivery" badge
        → No: "Pay All Now" active
    → Click "Pay All Now"
        → Create bulk Razorpay order (sum of all dues)
        → Razorpay modal → User pays
        → [Atomic transaction]: 
            UPDATE laundry payments → completed
            UPDATE marketplace_orders → payment_status=paid
        → All dues cleared → Redirect to home
```

### 5.5 Admin Workflow

```
Admin Dashboard → Overview (stats, revenue charts)
    → Customers tab → search/filter → block/approve Pay Later
    → Orders tab → filter by status/market → assign partner
    → Cancel order → [DELETE payment + release coupon + decrement partner load]
    → Returns → review photo → approve/decline
    → Marketplace → view/manage market orders
    → Broadcast notification to all customers
```

