## 6. System Architecture

### 6.1 Current Architecture (Monolith)

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                        CLIENT LAYER                          │
│  user/dashboard.php  │  delivery/dashboard.php  │ admin/*.php│
│         ↕ Fetch/POST JSON                                    │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
                              │
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                         API LAYER (PHP)                      │
│  api/auth.php  │  api/orders.php  │  api/payments.php       │
│  api/delivery.php  │  api/admin.php  │  api/invoice.php     │
│  api/marketplace_products.php  │  api/marketplace_orders.php│
│  api/update_marketplace_status.php  │  api/staff_requests.php│
│  api/create_marketplace_order.php   │  api/products.php     │
│         ↕ PDO Prepared Statements                            │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
                              │
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                    PERSISTENCE LAYER                         │
│           MySQL (XAMPP / MariaDB)                           │
│      15+ tables — orders, payments, marketplace, etc.       │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
                              │
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                    EXTERNAL SERVICES                         │
│  Razorpay (payments)  │  Firebase FCM (push)                │
│  Google OAuth (SSO)   │  Google Maps (navigation)           │
│  dompdf (PDF)         │  html5-qrcode (QR scan)             │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

### 6.2 Recommended Scalable Architecture (Target)

```
┌──────────────┐    ┌──────────────┐    ┌──────────────┐
│  Customer    │    │  Delivery    │    │   Admin      │
│  SPA (JS)   │    │  PWA (JS)    │    │  Dashboard   │
└──────┬───────┘    └──────┬───────┘    └──────┬───────┘
       │                   │                   │
       └───────────────────┼───────────────────┘
                           │ HTTPS REST API
                    ┌──────▼──────┐
                    │   PHP API   │  ← Add: nginx reverse proxy
                    │  Layer      │  ← Add: Redis session store
                    └──────┬──────┘  ← Add: Job queue (FCM async)
                           │
              ┌────────────┼────────────┐
              │            │            │
       ┌──────▼──┐  ┌──────▼──┐  ┌────▼─────┐
       │  MySQL  │  │  Redis  │  │ File Store│
       │(Primary)│  │ (Cache) │  │(S3/MinIO) │
       └─────────┘  └─────────┘  └──────────┘
```

### 6.3 Tech Stack Assessment

| Layer | Current | Recommended Upgrade |
|-------|---------|---------------------|
| Backend | PHP 8 (procedural) | PHP 8.2+ with slim routing (keep simple) |
| Database | MySQL / MariaDB | MySQL 8 with proper indexes ← ADD NOW |
| Cache | None | Redis for session + catalog caching |
| Queue | Synchronous (FCM in request) | Async queue for FCM + PDF gen |
| File Storage | Local `/uploads/` | MinIO or S3 (for auth-controlled access) |
| Frontend | Vanilla JS SPA | Current is fine — add service worker for offline |
| Deployment | XAMPP | VPS (Ubuntu) + nginx + MySQL + PHP-FPM |
| CI/CD | None | GitHub Actions → SSH deploy |

