## 8. API Structure

### 8.1 API Conventions

- **Method:** All mutating operations use `POST` with JSON body
- **Auth:** Session-based (`$_SESSION['user_id']` + `role`)
- **CSRF:** All POST endpoints validate `X-CSRF-Token` header via `hash_equals()`
- **Response format:** `{ "success": bool, "message": string, ...data }`

### 8.2 API Endpoints Reference

| File | Action Key | Method | Auth Role | Description |
|------|-----------|--------|-----------|-------------|
| `api/auth.php` | `google_auth` | POST | Public | Google OAuth login/register |
| `api/auth.php` | `otp_login` | POST | Public | Phone OTP verification |
| `api/auth.php` | `logout` | POST | Any | Destroy session |
| `api/orders.php` | `get_dashboard_stats` | POST | customer | Summary counts + recent order |
| `api/orders.php` | `get_orders` | POST | customer | Paginated order list with items |
| `api/orders.php` | `create_order` | POST | customer | Place laundry order |
| `api/orders.php` | `cancel_order` | POST | customer | Cancel pending/assigned order |
| `api/orders.php` | `apply_coupon` | POST | customer | Validate + apply coupon |
| `api/orders.php` | `submit_return` | POST | customer | Submit return request with photo |
| `api/orders.php` | `request_pay_later` | POST | customer | Apply for Pay Later plan |
| `api/orders.php` | `set_auto_order` | POST | customer | Configure weekly auto-pickup |
| `api/payments.php` | `create_razorpay_order` | POST | customer | Init Razorpay order for checkout |
| `api/payments.php` | `verify_payment` | POST | customer | Verify Razorpay signature + mark paid |
