## 9. UI/UX Recommendations

### 9.1 Critical UX Bugs to Fix

| # | Issue | Location | Fix |
|---|-------|----------|-----|
| 1 | Cancelled marketplace orders appear in pending dues | Payments tab | ✅ Fixed (status != 'cancelled' filter) |
| 2 | "Pay All Now" missing when only marketplace dues exist | Payments tab | ✅ Fixed (removed early-exit guard) |
| 3 | Toast notifications unstyled in dashboard | dashboard.php | ✅ Fixed (injected CSS) |
| 4 | Customer phone shown in delivery dashboard before dispatch | Pickup tab | Verify visibility guard is applied |
| 5 | Cart total doesn't update on per-meter price change | Marketplace cart | Already working — monitor |
| 6 | No mobile sidebar navigation in marketplace | marketplace.php | Add hamburger nav for <768px |

### 9.2 UX Improvements Recommended

1. **Payment Status Clarity:** Show a "🔒 Waiting for Delivery" explanation tooltip so users understand why "Pay All Now" is locked
2. **Order Timeline Accessibility:** Add ARIA roles to the timeline dots for screen reader compatibility
3. **Empty State Improvement:** Marketplace empty cart has a "Start Shopping" CTA — apply same pattern to empty order history
4. **Delivery Verification UX:** For the marketplace PIN flow, show a countdown timer on the customer's PIN (since it rotates every 30 minutes)
5. **Bulk Payment Breakdown:** After successful bulk payment, show a detailed receipt: "₹X paid for 2 laundry orders + ₹Y for 1 marketplace order"
6. **Profile Completeness Indicator:** Percentage complete bar in sidebar (50% → 100% as they fill fields)

