| MKT-19 | Stock decremented on order placement | `stock -= qty` in DB | +ve |
| MKT-20 | Stock restored on cancellation | `stock += qty` restored | +ve |

### 10.3 Acceptance Criteria (Key Flows)

**Combined Payment Flow**
- ✅ Cancelled orders never appear in payment dues
- ✅ Marketplace-only users see "Pay All Now" (not blocked by absence of laundry dues)
- ✅ In-transit orders lock the bulk payment button with visible reason
- ✅ Payment atomically marks both laundry + marketplace orders as paid in one Razorpay transaction

**Marketplace Delivery PIN**
- ✅ "Mark Delivered" button replaced by "Verify PIN to Deliver" for out_for_delivery marketplace orders
- ✅ Same OTP modal used for both laundry and marketplace (isMarket flag routes to correct API)
- ✅ PIN validated server-side using same `crc32(user_id + salt + window)` algorithm used on customer dashboard
- ✅ Previous 30-min window accepted for graceful expiry

