## 12. Deployment Strategy

### 12.1 Current (Development)
- XAMPP on Windows local machine
- Accessible on local network `http://192.168.x.x/dashboard/DigiWash`
- No SSL, no process management, no backups

### 12.2 Recommended Production Setup

```
Internet
    │
    ▼
[ Cloudflare DNS + DDoS Protection ]
    │
    ▼
[ Ubuntu 22.04 VPS — nginx ]
    │
    ├── /etc/nginx/sites-available/digiwash.conf
    │       server_name digiwash.yourdomain.com;
    │       ssl_certificate (Let's Encrypt);
    │       root /var/www/digiwash;
    │       location / { try_files $uri $uri/ /index.php?$query_string; }
    │
    ├── PHP 8.2-FPM
    ├── MySQL 8 (localhost)
    └── Redis (session + cache)
```

### 12.3 Deployment Checklist

```
Pre-deployment:
  [ ] All CRITICAL security issues fixed
  [ ] .env file excluded from git (.gitignore)
  [ ] RAZORPAY keys switched to LIVE mode
  [ ] FIREBASE_VAPID_KEY set for production domain
  [ ] Database indexes applied
  [ ] Error reporting disabled (display_errors = Off)
  [ ] SSL/HTTPS enforced (redirect HTTP → HTTPS)
  [ ] /uploads/ protected or moved outside webroot
  [ ] cron.php secured with secret token
  [ ] cron job scheduled: */5 * * * * curl "https://domain/cron.php?token=SECRET"

Post-deployment:
  [ ] Run a test order end-to-end (COD + Online + Pay Later)
  [ ] Verify Razorpay webhook receives payment events
  [ ] Test FCM push notification on real device
  [ ] Verify PDF invoice downloads
  [ ] Run OWASP ZAP scan on production URL
```

### 12.4 CI/CD Pipeline (GitHub Actions)

```yaml
# .github/workflows/deploy.yml
on:
  push:
    branches: [main]
jobs:
  deploy:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    steps:
      - uses: actions/checkout@v3
      - name: Run PHPUnit tests
        run: vendor/bin/phpunit
      - name: Deploy via SSH
        run: |
          rsync -avz --exclude='.env' --exclude='vendor/' . user@server:/var/www/digiwash/
          ssh user@server "cd /var/www/digiwash && composer install --no-dev"
```

