## 13. Business Model & Future Scope

### 13.1 Current Revenue Potential

| Stream | Model | Estimate |
|--------|-------|---------|
| Laundry SaaS | Per-merchant monthly fee | ₹200-500/merchant/month |
| Marketplace commission | 5-10% on each marketplace order | Variable |
| Pay Later interest | 0-2% processing fee on credit settlement | Variable |
| White-label licensing | License DigiWash to other laundry businesses | ₹50K-2L per setup |

### 13.2 Scalability Milestones

| Stage | Users | Infrastructure |
|-------|-------|---------------|
| **Phase 1 (Now)** | 1 market, 50 merchants | XAMPP / Single VPS |
| **Phase 2 (3 months)** | 3 markets, 200 merchants | VPS + MySQL tuning + Redis |
| **Phase 3 (6 months)** | 10 markets, 1000 merchants | Load balanced, CDN for assets |
| **Phase 4 (12 months)** | Multi-city SaaS | Microservices, multi-tenant DB |

